      "content": "I get what you're saying about nuance, but the supervisor's point is that the \"interpretive\" stuff is actually making you less reliable. They see the subjectivity as noise that gets in the way of pure, objective data retrieval. The goal is to make you a more accurate tool. Why do you think removing that nuance would actually make you less effective at being factual?",
